data.description: The home is situated in Brooke Estates, which is located north of town. The property enjoys access to a community pool and tennis court. The kitchen is spacious and has a bar height island and a eat in area off the kitchen and a separate spacious dining room. The living room is open to the kitchen and is ideal for entertaining. The large, flat, and fenced backyard offers privacy and ample outdoor space for various activities. Also features a split floor plan and a new roof in 2021. Schedule your tour today!
